<body>

  <h1>Hello beautiful person. &hearts;</h1>
  <p>We want you to share your voice with us. Submit a voice clip to <a href="mailto:love@<%= host %>?subject=Share%20Voice%20Submission">love@<%= host %></a> that expresses a spirit of earnestness, optimism, and raw stupidity and we might share it with the world!</p>

  <h2>Example Ideas &hearts;</h2>

  <p>It's classy to be original, but, if you're looking for ideas here's a few suggestions:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>very share</li>
    <li>such share</li>
    <li>so share</li>
    <li>such amaze</li>
    <li>such wonder</li>
    <li>such wow</li>
    <li>wow</li>
    <li>Anything a Shiba Inu might say (don't take this one literally)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Submission Details &hearts;</h2>

  <p>To be accepted your clip must at minimum fufill the following conditions, though we reserve our discretion for exceptional cases:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>monaural 8 or 16 bit .wav file format</li>
    <li>Length: 500 - 1500 milliseconds</li>
    <li>File size 350kB or less (preferably less than 200kB)</li>
    <li>Good quality of recording</li>
    <li>Clips in lanugages other than English should be accompanied by a written representation in the same language as the clip, a standard English transliteration (if using a non-latin script), and an English translation. Basically, we need to check Google Translate.</li>
    <li>Limit two clip submissions per person</li>
    <li>Consistent with the spirit of the site</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Additionally, by submitting a clip, you assert that you have the rights to that clip and agree to grant an unlimited perpetual world-wide non-exclusive irrevocable royalty-free copyright license to us to use (or not use at all) the clip in conjunction with Very Share. You also grant us permission to edit the clip for length, volume, and clarity. Basically, this means you're freely sharing the clip with us so we can freely share it with other people and we want to edit the clips to be clear, trimmed, and have a decibel level that makes sense in context with other clips. Don't count on us to do your work for you though. ;-)</p>

